pull.title: Wshadow: Do not shadow argument with a local variable
pull.body:
Current master adds new `-Wshadow` warning:

```
wallet/rpcdump.cpp:801:44: warning: declaration shadows a local variable [-Wshadow]
```

Use better name for the local variable, matching its vector type.

issue.title: Enable -Wshadow by default
issue.body:
Test and enabled `-Wshadow` by default, add developer note about this change (see #8105).

As my native language is not English, I'm open to suggestions.

[Edits from maintainers allowed for easier cooperation.]
